Package ohos.nfc.tag

Class MifareUltralightTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.nfc.tag.TagManager
      • ohos.nfc.tag.MifareUltralightTag

  • public class MifareUltralightTag
extends TagManager
    Provides interfaces to create a MIFARE Ultralight tag and perform I/O operations on the tag.

    This class inherits from the TagManager abstract class and provides interfaces to create a MIFARE Ultralight tag, obtain the tag type, and read and write pages of the tag.

    Since:
    3
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Communication#NFC

    • Method Detail

      • getInstance

        public static MifareUltralightTag getInstance​(TagInfo tagInfo)
        Obtains a MifareUltralightTag object based on the given tag information.

        During tag reading, if the tag supports the NFC-A technology, a MifareUltralightTag object will be created based on the given tag information.

        Parameters:
        tagInfo - Indicates the information about the given tag.
        Returns:
        Returns the MifareUltralightTag object.
        Since:
        3

      • getMifareType

        public int getMifareType​()
        Obtains the type of the MIFARE Ultralight tag. The type can be MIFARE_ULTRALIGHT, MIFARE_ULTRALIGHT_C, or MIFARE_UNKNOWN.
        Returns:
        Returns the type of the MIFARE Ultralight tag.
        Since:
